Team

 






                            
                                Saul Richter                            


                            Managing Partner                        



Saul is a co-founder of Rittenhouse Ventures and has been active within the technology community for twenty-five years as a venture capitalist, start-up entrepreneur, and technologist.
Saul has a strong background in software development and systems administration, and has been investing in the healthcare technology space for over fifteen years.
Saul has a passion for emerging technologies, and enjoys supporting entrepreneurs throughout a company’s growth process.
 
