                                Steve Holstad                            


                            Chief Financial Officer                        



Steve is the CFO for Rittenhouse Ventures, while serving as the Managing Director for Strattech Partners, LLC, based in Devon, PA, which was founded in 2000 as a business consulting and venture capital firm.
Over the past 15 years, Steve has been the acting CFO for a number of venture-backed firms in the Philadelphia region.
Steve has nearly 30 years of finance and operational experience across companies in commercial banking, energy, chemical, and venture-backed technology.
 
