General Partner

                                    Prior                


Edison Venture Fund LP


                  Edison Venture Fund LP invests in technology companies located in the US. The fund targets companies operating in the fields of application & system software, environmental technology & services, healthcare products & services, communications products & services, computer equipment & services, education technology, electronic components & systems, office & factory automation, biotechnology equipment & services, analytical instrumentation, specialty chemicals & materials, financial services, consumer products & services, and energy & agricultural technologies. It provides financing for expansion/later stage, MBOs and special situations such as sale of family owned businesses, divestitures, spinouts. It selectively invests in start-ups and also considers secondary stock purchases from existing shareholders.                




Vice President

                                    Prior                


Columbia Capital LLC - Virginia


                  Columbia Capital specializes in investments in emerging companies in the wireless, broadband, media and enterprise information technology sectors. Within the wireless sector, the firm focuses on mobile carriers, towers, network infrastructure, software, applications, media services and components. Their investments in the broadband sector include next generation carriers, software, infrastructure and components. Columbia Capital's enterprise information technology investments focus on managed services, information technology services, software and information management. Within the media sector, they target companies involved in cable, broadcasting, consumer Internet, advertising and content.Columbia Capital looks for companies with exceptional management teams that are focused on defining markets and developing disruptive technologies. The firm looks for under-the-radar opportunities, out-of-favor companies, value plays and turnaround situations. Their main focus is on growth-oriented new market development, but they are also interested in investments in established companies that offer attractive investment opportunities. Columbia Capital seeks to identify markets with the potential for rapid growth. They also look for transformational opportunities and seek to leverage their market experience to develop business models and distribution strategies that increase the chances for break-out success.Columbia Capital participates in early stage investments, large growth stage financings and special situations. Investments range from seed investments of $1 million to late-stage capital investments of $50 million or more. The firm is typically the first institutional investor in their portfolio companies. They take a leadership role in their portfolio companies and on their portfolio companies' boards of directors.                




Vice President

                                    Prior                


Columbia Capital LLC


                  Columbia Capital LLC is a registered investment advisor located in Fullerton, California.                




